snippet.title: Prison Architect: Gangs - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Your Prison. Their Rules.

Prison Architect: Gangs introduces Gang warfare. Bring order to your prison and manage its boiling point by reforming gang members and protecting your inmates and staff.

The seventh expansion for Prison Architect is coming soon, wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1948120/Prison_Architect__Gangs
